cset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/andre-3000-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/andre-3000-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/andre-3000-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/andre-3000-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/andre-3000-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/andre-3000-Taylor-Hill_Getty-Images-for-Live-Nation-Urban-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/andre-3000">André 3000</a>分享了他对最新一波说唱歌手的看法，认为他们中的很多人“听起来都一样”。</p><p>这位亚特兰大嘻哈传奇人物与<a href="/artists/sexyy-red">性感红 (Sexyy Red)</a>等人一起出现在<a href="/artists/lebron-james">勒布朗·詹姆斯 (LeBron James)</a>和马弗里克·卡特 (Maverick Carter) 的<em>The Shop</em>播客的最新一集中。他被问及他数十年的音乐生涯，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-announces-first-solo-album-in-17-years-full-of-flute-music-preorder-3538764">他最近的首张爵士专辑《New Blue Sun》</a> 。</p><p>在上传到 Instagram 的一段视频中，3000 谈到了<a href="/artists/outkast">OutKast</a>在 Dungeon Family 中的时光——该家族的领导者是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rico-wade-outkast-collaborator-and-organized-noize-member-dies-at-52-3617600">已故的 Organized Noize 传奇人物 Rico Wade，</a>他于今年四月因心力衰竭去世——导致他说当今的说唱明星“没有时间”来修炼自己”。</p><p> “如果当我们认为自己已经准备好时就以 OutKast 的身份出现，我们今天就不会出现了，因为我们听起来和其他人一样。我们听起来就像我们正在听的人一样，”他推测道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9nJ3GbP8wW/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; pad